sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant AuthDB as Auth DB
    participant Mailer as Mailer

    Note over KH,Mailer: BUOC 1 - Yeu cau ma OTP

    KH->>GW: POST /api/auth/forgot-password
    Note over KH,GW: email
    GW->>Auth: Forward request

    activate Auth
    Auth->>AuthDB: findAllByEmail(email)
    AuthDB-->>Auth: danh sach accounts

    alt Khong tim thay email
        Note over Auth: Luon tra success de tranh lo thong tin
        Auth-->>GW: 200 OK
        GW-->>KH: Neu email ton tai, ma xac nhan da duoc gui
    else Tim thay it nhat 1 account
        Auth->>Auth: Tao OTP 6 chu so ngau nhien
        Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.hash(OTP, salt=10)

        loop Moi account co cung email
            Auth->>AuthDB: resetToken.deleteAllByAccountId
            Auth->>AuthDB: resetToken.create - het han 15 phut
        end

        Auth->>Mailer: sendResetCode(email, OTP)
        Mailer-->>KH: Email chua ma OTP 6 chu so

        Auth-->>GW: 200 OK
        GW-->>KH: Neu email ton tai, ma xac nhan da duoc gui
    end
    deactivate Auth

    Note over KH,Mailer: BUOC 2 - Dat lai mat khau

    KH->>GW: POST /api/auth/reset-password
    Note over KH,GW: email, code OTP, newPassword
    GW->>Auth: Forward request

    activate Auth
    Auth->>AuthDB: findAllByEmail(email)
    AuthDB-->>Auth: danh sach accounts

    alt Email khong ton tai
        Auth-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>KH: Yeu cau khong hop le
    else Tim thay accounts
        loop Tim token hop le trong cac accounts
            Auth->>AuthDB: resetToken.findLatestByAccountId
            AuthDB-->>Auth: token record
            Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.compare(code, token_hash)
        end

        alt OTP sai hoac het han
            Auth-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
            GW-->>KH: Ma xac nhan khong hop le hoac da het han
        else OTP dung
            Auth->>Auth: bcrypt.hash(newPassword, salt=10)

            loop Cap nhat tat ca accounts cung email
                Auth->>AuthDB: account.updatePassword
                Auth->>AuthDB: refreshToken.revokeAll
                Auth->>AuthDB: resetToken.markUsed
            end

            Auth-->>GW: 200 OK
            GW-->>KH: Dat lai mat khau thanh cong
        end
    end
    deactivate Auth

